technology, media, and consumer goods converge.\",\"p2\":\"Our central holding provides strategic direction, capital allocation, and shared resources, allowing our divisions to focus purely on disrupting their respective markets.\",\"link\":\"Learn more about our vision\"},\"subsidiaries\":{\"title\":\"Our Ecosystem\",\"investors_link\":\"View Investor Relations\",\"forge\":{\"name\":\"Arasue Forge\",\"description\":\"Great ideas mean nothing if they stay in the air. Arasue Forge is the development studio where advanced software and critical tech come to life with precision, power, and flawless performance. We build the digital infrastructure that defines industries.\",\"link\":\"Visit Forge\",\"tag\":\"Engineering with character.\"},\"labs\":{\"name\":\"Arasue Labs\",\"description\":\"True excellence accepts no shortcuts. Arasue Labs bridges scientific rigor with nature's purity, managing the import and logistics of premium products with absolute traceability. Unwavering quality, from the source to your hands.\",\"link\":\"Visit Labs\",\"tag\":\"Unaltered from the source.\"},\"media\":{\"name\":\"Arasue Media\",\"description\":\"In a sea of constant noise, we create depth. Arasue Media produces, publishes, and distributes high-fidelity content that captures attention and leaves a real mark. Powerful storytelling backed by sophisticated execution.\",\"link\":\"Visit Media\",\"tag\":\"Content with character.\"},\"protection\":{\"name\":\"Arasue Protection\",\"description\":\"Real success is never left to chance. Arasue Protection shields your life, health, and wealth with high-tier insurance solutions and absolute certainty. We protect your legacy so you can focus on building it.\",\"link\":\"Visit Protection\",\"tag\":\"Unconditional peace of mind.\"}},\"global\":{\"title\":\"Global Presence\",\"desc\":\"Operating seamlessly across North America and the world.\"},\"news\":{\"title\":\"Latest from the Newsroom\",\"link\":\"View All News\",\"tag\":\"Press Release\",\"article_title\":\"Arasue Horizon Announces Strategic Expansion into New Markets\",\"article_desc\":\"Read about our latest strategic acquisitions and how they align with our vision for the upcoming fiscal year.\"},\"leadership\":{\"title\":\"Leadership\",\"subtitle\":\"Guided by operators with a track record of asymmetric returns.\",\"josue_role\":\"Chief Executive Officer\",\"josue_desc\":\"Architect of the Arasue ecosystem. Focuses on capital allocation and long-term vision.\",\"elena_role\":\"Head of Forge\",\"elena_desc\":\"Former staff engineer at major tech firms. Leads product engineering and platform scale.\",\"marcus_role\":\"Head of Media\",\"marcus_desc\":\"Cultural strategist who has manufactured multiple global viral moments.\"},\"investor_form\":{\"title\":\"Investor Relations\",\"subtitle\":\"Request access to our quarterly thesis and financial disclosures.\",\"name\":\"Full Name\",\"firm\":\"Firm / Organization\",\"email\":\"Corporate Email\",\"type\":\"Investor Type\",\"type_vc\":\"Venture Capital\",\"type_pe\":\"Private Equity\",\"type_fo\":\"Family Office\",\"type_angel\":\"Angel / Individual\",\"type_other\":\"Other\",\"submit\":\"Request Access\",\"submitting\":\"Requesting...\",\"success\":\"Request Received. Our IR team will review and respond shortly.\"},\"philosophy\":{\"label\":\"Operating Philosophy\",\"statement_1\":\"We don't follow trends.\",\"statement_2\":\"We build infrastructure.\",\"statement_3\":\"Capital is merely a tool. Operational excellence is the outcome.\"},\"global_impact\":{\"title\":\"Global Footprint\",\"subtitle\":\"Architecting systems across borders. From the US to Latin America and beyond.\",\"stat_1_val\":\"3\",\"stat_1_lbl\":\"Core Hubs\",\"stat_2_val\":\"24/7\",\"stat_2_lbl\":\"Operations\",\"stat_3_val\":\"$$0\",\"stat_3_lbl\":\"Friction\"}},\"forge\":{\"hero\":{\"badge\":\"Premium Software Engineering\",\"title\":\"Premium Software, Crafted to Perfection\",\"subtitle\":\"We transform your boldest ideas into robust, scalable, and beautifully designed digital products.\",\"cta\":\"See our Services\",\"secondary_cta\":\"View Our Work\",\"cta_contact\":\"Book a Call\"},\"ticker\":{\"trusted\":\"Powered by industry-leading technologies\"},\"services\":{\"title\":\"Our Expertise\",\"web_dev\":{\"title\":\"Web Development\",\"desc\":\"Custom, high-performance web-scrolling experiences.\"},\"brand_web\":{\"title\":\"Personal Brand Web\",\"desc\":\"From Instagram to Web: A premium landing page for your brand.\"},\"meta_ads\":{\"title\":\"Meta Ads Audit\",\"desc\":\"Deep analysis and optimization of your advertising campaigns.\"},\"seo_audit\":{\"title\":\"SEO Audit\",\"desc\":\"Technical and content audit to dominate search results.\"},\"automations\":{\"title\":\"N8N Automations\",\"desc\":\"Save hundreds of hours with custom workflow automations.\"},\"pm\":{\"title\":\"Project Management\",\"desc\":\"Independent consulting and project leadership.\"}},\"work\":{\"title\":\"Featured Work\",\"subtitle\":\"We build scalable architectures and beautiful interfaces that drive real business metrics.\",\"project1_category\":\"Fintech Platform\",\"project1_title\":\"Global Payment Dashboard\",\"project1_desc\":\"A complete overhaul of a legacy financial dashboard, migrating to Next.js and Tailwind to improve load times by 400% and user retention by 35%.\",\"project2_category\":\"E-Commerce App\",\"project2_title\":\"Premium Retail Experience\",\"project2_desc\":\"Native-feeling headless commerce application using React Native and Shopify Storefront API. Increased mobile conversion rates by over 120%.\"},\"process\":{\"title\":\"How We Work\",\"subtitle\":\"We don't just write code; we engineer solutions designed to scale from day one.\",\"step1\":\"Discovery & Strategy\",\"step1_desc\":\"We analyze your business needs and craft a tailored technical plan.\",\"arch_title\":\"Architecture & Design\",\"arch_desc\":\"We design scalable system architectures and beautiful UI/UX that align with your business goals.\",\"step2\":\"Development & Delivery\",\"step2_desc\":\"Agile building, rigorous testing, and a flawless launch.\",\"step3\":\"Growth & Maintenance\",\"step3_desc\":\"We ensure your product scales efficiently.\"},\"pricing\":{\"title\":\"Transparent SaaS Pricing\",\"setup\":\"Setup\",\"mo\":\"/mo\",\"one_time\":\"One-time\",\"retainer\":\"Retainer (mo)\",\"features\":\"Includes hosting, updates, and priority support.\"},\"testimonials\":{\"text1\":\"Arasue Forge transformed our entire digital infrastructure. Their architecture allowed us to scale from 10k to 500k monthly active users without a single hiccup.\",\"author1\":\"Sarah Jenkins\",\"role1\":\"CTO, Vertex Analytics\",\"text2\":\"The sheer speed and quality of their React development is unmatched. They don't just build apps, they build products that people love to use.\",\"author2\":\"David Chen\",\"role2\":\"Founder, Elevate\"},\"cta\":{\"title\":\"Ready to build?\",\"subtitle\":\"Stop compromising on your engineering quality. Partner with us and scale your digital products today.\",\"note\":\"Reply within 24 hours. No obligations.\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Frequently Asked Questions\",\"q1\":\"Do you offer custom development outside these plans?\",\"a1\":\"Yes, we handle enterprise-grade custom applications. Contact us for a custom quote.\",\"q2\":\"What technologies do you use?\",\"a2\":\"We specialize in the React ecosystem (Next.js), Node.js, and cloud-native architectures.\",\"q3\":\"How does the SaaS web model work?\",\"a3\":\"Instead of a massive upfront cost, you pay a small setup fee and a monthly subscription that covers hosting, maintenance, and minor updates forever.\"},\"services_page\":{\"title\":\"Engineered for Dominance\",\"subtitle\":\"We don't just build websites. We build scalable systems that dominate your market.\",\"scarcity\":\"Due to our high-touch process, we only onboard 3 new clients per quarter.\"},\"portfolio_page\":{\"title\":\"Our Work\",\"subtitle\":\"Case studies of scalable digital products.\"},\"pricing_page\":{\"title\":\"Transparent, Scale-Ready Pricing\",\"subtitle\":\"No hidden fees. Premium infrastructure packaged into predictable models.\",\"anchoring_text\":\"While traditional agencies charge $50k+ upfront, our SaaS model guarantees zero technical debt for a fraction of the cost.\"},\"contact_page\":{\"title\":\"Start Your Build\",\"subtitle\":\"Schedule a discovery session with our senior architects.\"},\"process_section\":{\"title\":\"How We Build\",\"subtitle\":\"An uncompromising approach to engineering.\",\"steps\":[{\"title\":\"Architecture Discovery\",\"desc\":\"We map out the precise technical requirements, data models, and infrastructure needs.\"},{\"title\":\"System Design\",\"desc\":\"Creating scalable database schemas and high-fidelity wireframes that convert.\"},{\"title\":\"Engineering Sprints\",\"desc\":\"Rapid, agile development using Next.js and robust cloud architectures.\"},{\"title\":\"Deployment & Scale\",\"desc\":\"Zero-downtime deployment, QA, and continuous performance optimization.\"}]},\"estimator_section\":{\"title\":\"Project Estimator\",\"subtitle\":\"Get an immediate baseline for your custom software or enterprise digital transformation.\",\"complexity\":\"Scope Complexity\",\"timeline\":\"Timeline Urgency\",\"min\":\"MVP / Web App\",\"max\":\"Enterprise Ecosystem\",\"options\":[{\"id\":\"relaxed\",\"label\":\"Standard (3-4 Months)\"},{\"id\":\"rush\",\"label\":\"Rush (8-10 Weeks)\"}],\"total\":\"Estimated Investment\",\"note\":\"*Estimate based on current availability. Final scope requires a discovery session.\",\"cta\":\"Request Formal Proposal\",\"submitting\":\"Requesting...\",\"success\":\"Proposal requested. We will contact you soon.\",\"emailPrompt\":\"Enter your work email to receive the proposal:\"}},\"media\":{\"hero\":{\"title\":\"Shaping Digital Culture\",\"subtitle\":\"Arasue Media is a powerhouse of content creation, streaming, and digital storytelling.\",\"cta\":\"Watch Latest\",\"cta_contact\":\"Partner with Us\"},\"services\":{\"title\":\"Our Capabilities\",\"content\":\"Content Production\",\"streams\":\"Live Streaming\",\"branding\":\"Digital Branding\"},\"work_page\":{\"title\":\"Selected Campaigns\",\"subtitle\":\"High-voltage content that shapes digital culture.\"},\"creators_page\":{\"title\":\"The Roster\",\"subtitle\":\"Our exclusive network of digital talent and producers.\"},\"contact_page\":{\"title\":\"Collaborate\",\"subtitle\":\"Ready to go viral? Let's talk strategy.\"}},\"labs\":{\"hero\":{\"title\":\"Nature Meets Science\",\"subtitle\":\"Premium organic products, sustainably sourced and meticulously crafted.\",\"cta\":\"Shop Collection\"},\"products\":{\"title\":\"Our Collection\",\"honey\":{\"title\":\"Raw Organic Honey\",\"desc\":\"100% pure, unpasteurized honey sourced directly from our reserves.\"},\"wellness\":{\"title\":\"Wellness Extracts\",\"desc\":\"Potent organic tinctures and health supplements.\"}},\"shop_page\":{\"title\":\"The Apothecary\",\"subtitle\":\"Limited-batch organic harvests. Taste the untouched nature.\"},\"story_page\":{\"title\":\"Our Origins\",\"subtitle\":\"From deep forests to premium extracts. The journey of Arasue Labs.\"},\"contact_page\":{\"title\":\"Wholesale & Support\",\"subtitle\":\"Reach out for bulk orders and premium partnerships.\"}},\"corporate\":{\"about\":{\"title\":\"Our Mission\",\"content\":\"Arasue Horizon is dedicated to building scalable ecosystems across software, media, and sustainability.\"},\"investors\":{\"title\":\"Investor Relations\",\"content\":\"Access our latest financial reports, governance documents, and shareholder information.\"},\"newsroom\":{\"title\":\"Newsroom\",\"content\":\"Latest updates, press releases, and media resources from Arasue Horizon.\"},\"contact\":{\"title\":\"Global Headquarters\",\"content\":\"Partner with Arasue Horizon. Direct lines to our investment and PR teams.\",\"form\":{\"name_lbl\":\"Full Name\",\"email_lbl\":\"C